description:
Create a function that simulates a dice roll:

function rollDice() {
  // Returns a promise that resolves after 1 second
  // Resolves with a random number 1-6
}

Use it like:
rollDice()
  .then(result => console.log('Rolled:', result));

Hint: Use Math.floor(Math.random() * 6) + 1 for random 1-6

