commonMistakes.correction:
Forgetting to return a promise from a function:
   function getData() {
     new Promise((resolve) => { ... });  // WRONG - not returned!
   }

   function getData() {
     return new Promise((resolve) => { ... });  // CORRECT
   }

Not returning in .then() for chaining:
   promise
     .then(data => {
       processData(data);  // Returns undefined!
     })
     .then(result => {
       console.log(result);  // undefined
     });

   Must return:
   .then(data => {
     return processData(data);
   })
